Interface DeepCloneable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - is the type you want cloned object to be
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTTPBasicHeadersFilter, HTTPContentFilter, HTTPFormDataFilter, HTTPHostFilter, HTTPPacket, HTTPPacketFilter, HTTPRequest, HTTPResponse

    public interface DeepCloneable<T>
    Interface used for providing a method to deep clone objects.
    Author:
    Ruben Christoffer

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      T cloneDeep()
      Creates a deep clone of this instance.

    • Method Detail

      • cloneDeep

        T cloneDeep()
        Creates a deep clone of this instance. That means that this object and any possible sub-objects have unique values.
        Returns:
        Deep-cloned object
